               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18480403-name-430" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18480403-name-430" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18480403-name-430" type="surname" value="BURDEN"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18480403-name-430" type="given" value="THOMAS"></interp>THOMAS BURDEN.</persName>
                  </hi> I live at Store-street, Bedford-square, in the parish of St. Giles'-in-the-Fields. On Friday evening, 10th March, I was in the passage, and saw the prisoner coming down stairs with a cash-box under his arm—I did not know him before, and asked where he had been—he said he had been to see <hi rend="italic">Mistress.</hi>—, but could say no more—he dropped the box, and tried to get away—I secured him, and sent for a policeman—he went down or his knees, and begged me to forgive him—I gave him in charge—I saw the box opened at the station—it contained purses, rings, and 2<hi rend="italic">l</hi>. 9<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. 10<hi rend="italic">d</hi>. in cash—this is it—(<hi rend="italic">produced.</hi>)</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner. Q.</hi> Did not I tell you a gentleman gave it me in the first floor? <hi rend="italic">A.</hi> No.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18480403-name-431" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18480403-name-431" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18480403-name-431" type="surname" value="BURDEN"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18480403-name-431" type="given" value="ELIZABETH"></interp>ELIZABETH BURDEN.</persName>
                  </hi> I live with my brother. This box, and contents are mine—it is worth 8<hi rend="italic">l</hi>. at least—it was kept on the dressing-table in the second floor bed-room—the door was not locked—there was nobody up stairs.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner. Q.</hi> Were you up stairs? <hi rend="italic">A.</hi> was in the parlour, heard a noise, came out, and saw you on your knees—you only asked for mercy—you said nothing about a gentleman.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
