                        <interp inst="t18480403-name-432" type="given" value="WILLIAM"></interp>WILLIAM DIXON</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">policeman.</hi>) I was called to Mr. Burden's—the prisoner was given into my charge, and the box—he tried to get away.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence.</hi> I had not left work a quarter of an hour; a man,</p>
               <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="184804030045"></xptr>
               <p>standing at the door, asked me to carry a box; I said, "Yes," and he took me to the second floor, gave it me, and said, "If you see my brother down stairs, go on."</p>
